          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-12668 ec: additional ec tests",
        "message": "LU-12668 ec: additional ec tests\n\nThis patch adds an additional 22 tests which cover:\n\nEC layout operations (migration, split, truncate,\nfallocate), error rejection for invalid EC component\nchanges, lfs find with parity flags, multi-stripe data\nintegrity, PFL lazy parity instantiation, and failure\ninjection scenarios (OST stop/restart recovery, write\nfailures during parity resync, exceeding parity\ntolerance).\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nTest-Parameters: testlist=sanity-ec ostcount=8\nSigned-off-by: Maximilian Dilger <mdilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I8adfaed197e1509a2401dcdbf41c65596c40ae63\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
